Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}１洪都拉斯木紋龜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}２南部錦箱龜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}３圓澳龜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選２
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}答案是 ３哦 全世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你還沒睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從明天開始要去學校了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上也要考試了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都請了三天假了 所以回學校了要好好問問同學們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試的範圍啦 課程內容什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要敷衍我！之前的考試也沒取得好成績的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 老媽真是囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且期末考試的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是明天嗎！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\bord0\shad0\frz6.572\pos(716,366)\c&H3A525F&}中\N獎\N了\N\N才\N怪\N呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…太遲了！！你的忠告來的太遲了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你老是躺在被窩裡沒學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學了啊！邊睡邊學了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你學了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底學沒學啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是在討論你忠告來遲了的問題吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我忠告你之後你會學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是掛科的話老娘就滅了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太極端了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Ultra Great Delicious Wonderful完蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：又是森林好小子中洛基的Super Ultra Great Delicious Wonderful Punch的捏他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 放手一搏吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離去學校的時間大概還有10小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的是明天的考試是英語和音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就能把精力集中到英語一科上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 現在我需要的是和昨天廢柴的我告別&集中力！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了能毫無遺憾的送走今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑著度過明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算昨天滴落過淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算至今無數次被擊垮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直笑著面對這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著往遠處的船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著遠處的光輝不斷奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是奔跑 奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是解開束縛的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一首好詩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很帥的東西！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工廠大叔的羞澀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先碰碰運氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知道英語考試範圍的現在 只有賭一把了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是英語單詞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 參上！
