Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love把我的愛~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 總會別離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmation(組成)你的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,teleportation (傳送) 現在正穿越時空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosmos(宇宙) 穿過無盡的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight submarine(午夜潛艇) 想與你一起乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever 永遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever 與你永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever直到時間盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是詩麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在學習已經太遲了什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚呼 真是的完蛋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被老媽殺了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏今天感冒好了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒明明比被殺好上一百倍的說！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少… 多感冒三天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想考試的話 只要重新得感冒就行了嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔！好痛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 這樣的話肯定能成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是在病剛好的時候就洗冰水澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊病肯定會復發的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來！快來~！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很順利嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是要忍耐的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有度過了這個難關…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能走上勝利的康莊大道！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要重新發燒 就是我的勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上吃刨冰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把房間冷氣開到最強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不蓋被子說晚安~☆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然完全沒事哪！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 快起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體溫計！火柴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等於 升溫!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你已經起來了麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要去學校的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙 好燙 燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發…發燒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又舊病復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少度？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8… 88.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛弄壞它啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 是感冒了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很精神麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\fs66\pos(800,360)\blur8\bord2}大\N工\N財\N閥\N的\N力\N量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}水肯定很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦 提交社團申請書的截止日期是今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就要廢部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算申請通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去也會因為成員不足而真的廢部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事的話不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了 明天我請你喝果汁當謝禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 舉手之勞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 別客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的路上順便買攪拌機和蘋果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是大工財閥的力量麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒繩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不能做放到校長鞋櫃裡的稻草人了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來… 沒有最重要的稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去買… 又沒有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我零花錢的老婆不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.94,XD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\pos(631,421)}老婆、同窗旅行中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了但是米沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候真想喝白蘭地一醉方休
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 肝臟剛動過刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪神隊又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是為了環保還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買個芝士牛肉漢堡發現沒有芝士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己主頁的留言板完全沒人來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來昨天我組織的聊天大會也是參加的人一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人來這事讓我想起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我坐的巴士也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上車之後 所有人都下車了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部人都下車了這事 讓我想起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中時的修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老師~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\shad0\bord0\c&H2D3134&\fs30\frz32.13\pos(757,340)}修學旅行指南\N\N\N\N\N\N借宿於鐮倉民家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了熄燈的時間關了燈之後2分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問了一句「大家都還醒著麼」之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現所有人都睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了這事 讓我想起最近貌似有點失眠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逼著自己睡著不停地在睡前吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然都長奶油肚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物什麼的 讓我想起上個月的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然… 只有一個黃油卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種悲觀的想法都給我閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該想想快樂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 原來是君子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽去旅行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想著給你過來做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真是得救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安 小美又長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  今天就啥也別想陪孫子玩一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個 剛才我在公園做了個糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你吃也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子餓了吧 給你吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是用巧克力做的哦 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛是嘛 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的淚腺真是松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 廚房借用一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生不是只有不幸的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這樣的好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 全部是巧克力做的啦 快吃啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那個 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的~快吃哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦~吶 快點啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不猶豫地吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很幸福的泥土味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 外公倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡定 淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼過不去的坎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要殺了我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了~~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼玩意兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強力漿糊~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很強力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個倒在走廊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓名乃和阪本動彈不得~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做這種奇怪的惡作劇了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說誰會落入這種明顯得不行的陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是上鉤吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把我弄出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等下還有事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗 只要潑上水就能解開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快給我水啊 快去拿水過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到了吃點心的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那博士就先去吃點心了 告退了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧… 啊咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 現在咋辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗 阪本你真像蟑螂清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是笑我的時候麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不是跟我差不多！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 啊咧 啊咧咧~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是天譴吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你一直一直都在做壞事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 咋辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 阪本不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本…？阪本…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有水的話就解不開…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就不能吃點心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說不定這樣下去肚子會餓…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不能吃飯 說不定會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣確實會死的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名乃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說外面有35度呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 咱剛才拿著的漿糊咻地自己跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要潑上水的話呢 就能解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要潑上水的話… 名乃 名乃~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}水?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先站起來吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便在走廊躺著會把衣服弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 這個？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…手！！我的手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手 手——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H454746&\fs36\pos(878,555)}祝\N賀\N\N圍\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N出\N征\N縣\N大\N賽
