Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\blur8\bord2\pos(200,360)\frz270}MONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是… 大工財閥的力量麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110\fad(900,0)\fs66\c&HFAF9FB&\blur20\t(0,900,1\blur1)\bord0\shad4\pos(640,550)\4c&H74907A&\3c&HE0E7E1&}差強人意的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊 終於下雨了 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fs54\pos(1220,360)\shad2\4c&HE2E7E9&}接\N下\N來\N｀\N輪\N到\N阪\N本\N了\N哦\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是誰~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H222A23&\fs36\pos(548,594)}陀思妥耶夫斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是博士麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 露餡了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 與其說是露餡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是只有博士會做這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這次換名乃來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 誒…好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是誰~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲一家今天也很平靜~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 名乃 我猜對了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 猜對了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那 下次還輪到我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第一問開始就完全不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個像中了抹殺光線要消失一樣的角色是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用什麼單詞形容啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}註：ニフラム「抹殺光線」：勇者鬥惡龍3~7里能讓對方整隊消失在天際的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題…我好像做過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我問過櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個跟中了抹殺光線要消失了一樣的角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是老師畫的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個跟中了抹殺光線要消失一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！就是中了抹殺光線要消失了的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔！！不是這一段啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先冷靜下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜啊小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌張的話會的問題都會變得不會的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fly… 麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話衝擊力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 這已經不是考英語了是在考推理啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在的我能做到的只有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的怪物拿著網球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話剛才的那題就不是Monster了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼微妙的關聯啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剛才的答案擦掉 換個方向思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃呃！ 橡皮擦什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘無人道啊！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎 怎 怎麼辦啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我只好用手指擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然最值得擁有的還是朋友啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是鋼筆擦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會擦破的 這樣的話紙會被擦破的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是扯淡的時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣醬 有沒有普通的橡皮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 睡著了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩十分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間啊 時間不夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將心…歸於無…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸於無……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南無阿彌陀佛啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心裡一直下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\fs18\b0\pos(603,439)\c&H423E39&}振 翅 吧 ！ ！ \N\h\h\h\h\h總 之 就 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\blur8\bord2\pos(100,360)}打\N開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 裡面有封情書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧不會吧！！從哪來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著Q班的田中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！！ 去看看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鐵球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像泥土一樣沉睡著~呼呼~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在烈火中鑄就~叮堂~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回的日常是第十二話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて　歯を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間　午後10時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:50.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　たくさん　笑ったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさん　ときめいたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:56.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友達と　バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:59.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騒いでる　時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:02.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって　目が合う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}…偶然、だよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:11.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:17.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねえ　あしたも会えるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを　閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:24.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ　キミだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:27.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:31.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あー　恋　してんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:42.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして　こいごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:46.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あした　まだ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:53.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ゆめで　すぐ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:59.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒後 起床刷牙來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不覺間 已到晚十點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:50.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多歡樂事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激與緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:56.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和閨中密友 像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:59.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大聲吵又鬧 偶爾會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:02.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶爾瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}這也不過是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初戀什麼的難以說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:11.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因為我不是這樣的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:17.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}吶 我們明天 也會相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}將我的雙眼 合上了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:24.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}腦海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:27.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 開心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:31.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 陷入戀愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好開心 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:42.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次見面 我的愛慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:46.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的話 我們又見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}現在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:53.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在夢中很快 我們會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:59.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}現在晚安吧


